name: Mussel Monitoring Program
description: Data collected from the Mussel Monitoring Program. Information includes date collected, year, month, water temperature, mussel larvae concentration, mussel larvae minimum size, mussel larvae maximum size, mussel larvae pre set size (%), mussel larvae set size (%), Pseudo nitzschia cells), tunicate larvae - Ciona, tunicate larvae - Styela, Tunicate Larvae – Botryllus, Tunicate Larvae – Botrylloides.

name: Oyster Monitoring Program Results
description: Information collected from the Oyster Monitoring Program. Information includes sample collection site, date, time, water temperature, total oyster larvae, concentration, size range and larvae > 250. In the concentration L=Low M=Medium H=High V=Very High

name: Nova Scotia Marine Aquaculture Leases
description: File contains all issued marine aquaculture leases along the coast of Nova Scotia. Fisheries and Aquaculture also provides a mapping tool for this data at: http://novascotia.ca/fish/aquaculture/site-mapping-tool/
